Class InternshipWithdrawalDbMgr

java.lang.Object
InternshipWithdrawalDbMgr
public class InternshipWithdrawalDbMgr extends Object
Manages the collection of InternshipWithdrawalApplicant objects. Implements the singleton pattern and provides methods to add, remove, filter, sort, and retrieve withdrawal applicants.
